            <thetext>Steps to reproduces:

1) Type two or more lines of text
2) Add twice or more indents
3) Execute &quot;Ordered list&quot;

The indentation is *not* removed and every execution of &quot;Ordered List&quot; results in one outdent.

Desired behaviour: When inserting an ordererd/unordered list the indentation is first cleared to omit this wrong behaviour in IE. This will harmonize the behaviour with Firefox browsers.</thetext>
